data.description: CHRISTMAS SPECIAL!  SELLER PAID 3-2-1 BUYDOWN with Interest Rate Starting at Approx. 3.25%! (FHA) Come See Your Almost New Home at Northridge in Traverse Mountain. Stunning Views of Utah Lake and the Valley from the Front Porch and Upstairs Bedrooms! Amazing Sunsets! Upgraded Kitchen with Double Ovens & Granite Countertops, Gas Fireplace, All w/ Walk-in -Closets, Laundry on 2nd Floor + Plumbed for 2nd Kitchen & Laundry in Basement. This Home Comes with All the Traverse Mountain Club House Amenities! Corner Lot on Quiet Street.  Priced to Sell at Under Appraised Value from August 2023 Appraisal.
